Skylight

Robert Carter 2011
rob@mintmedia.co.nz
http://createrevolutionaryart.net

An interactive installation for the The Edge, Auckland. 
Part of Digital Art Live, in association with the Aotea Centre, CoLab and AUT University.

Made using openframeworks, a toolkit for creative coding.
http://www.openframeworks.cc

Addons used:

ofxXmlSettings https://github.com/openframeworks/ofxXmlSettings
ofxDirList standard addon

Addons not used in the end that were helpful:
ofxFileLoader https://github.com/vtron/ofxVtron/tree/master/ofxFileLoader
ofxImageSequence https://github.com/Flightphase/ofxImageSequence
ofxRuiThread http://code.google.com/p/ruicode/
ofxOpenCv standard addon

Thanks to the people who answered my questions on the oF forums.

